<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-06-23T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-06-23T18:00:00-05:00" n="330" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d330">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">124.241/6–1347: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Embassy in Bolivia</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-06-23T19:00:00-04:00">June 23,
                                    1947—7 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>356. <gloss target="#t_urtel1">Urtel</gloss> 565, June 13.<note n="89" xml:id="d330fn1">Not printed.</note> Dept has no knowledge basis
                            belief lend-lease obligation would be reduced or cancelled. Possibly
                            some confusion arose because of fact payment requested of Bolivia is
                            only 18% of full value. Please make clear that Dept. expects payment in
                            dollars or Bolivianos of full equivalent of dollar indebtedness of
                            approximately $900,000.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>